videos.description: Darryl Morsell comes away with the steal, takes it the other way and feeds it to Olivier-Maxence Prosper for a dunk.

videos.description: Nate Watson cleans up Noah Horchler's missed 3-pointer from the corner with a powerful slam to give Providence the lead.
